description:
&lt;p&gt;Do you put patient care at the heart of everything you do? Are you committed to delivering quality, safe and efficient services which help people live their lives well?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen for 3 x Senior Physical Healthcare Nurse with current NMC registration (RGN/RSCN) to work as Band 6 Senior Physical Health Nurse in our Recovery teams. The post holder will work as part of the Recovery Team to provide a service to patients in mental health teams.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This post is subject to an enhanced with adults barred list Disclosure and Barring Service (DBS) Check. Successful candidates will either have a valid DBS check with the Trust or will be required to pay for the cost of the DBS Disclosure which is £47.50 for an enhanced disclosure and £29.50 for a standard disclosure, the cost of which will be deducted from first salary.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Name Amanda Brown&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Job title Operational Manager&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Email address amanda.brown3@nwbh.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
